column3: if the current wind speed is less than NUMBER_0 mph , tweet something .
column4: $dialogue @org.thingpedia.dialogue.transaction.execute ; now => ( @org.thingpedia.weather.current ) filter param:wind_speed <= NUMBER_0 unit:mph => notify ; now => @com.twitter.post ;

column3: if the wind speed is less than NUMBER_0 mph on the current weather report send a tweet .
column4: $dialogue @org.thingpedia.dialogue.transaction.execute ; now => ( @org.thingpedia.weather.current ) filter param:wind_speed <= NUMBER_0 unit:mph => notify ; now => @com.twitter.post ;

column3: show the current weather for a location , and if the wind speed there is less than NUMBER_0 miles per hour , then tweet something .
column4: $dialogue @org.thingpedia.dialogue.transaction.execute ; now => ( @org.thingpedia.weather.current ) filter param:wind_speed <= NUMBER_0 unit:mph => notify ; now => @com.twitter.post ;

column3: tweet something about the current weather if the wind speed is under NUMBER_0 miles per hour .
column4: $dialogue @org.thingpedia.dialogue.transaction.execute ; now => ( @org.thingpedia.weather.current ) filter param:wind_speed <= NUMBER_0 unit:mph => notify ; now => @com.twitter.post ;

column3: show the current weather for some place if the wind speed is less than NUMBER_0 mph and then tweet something .
column4: $dialogue @org.thingpedia.dialogue.transaction.execute ; now => ( @org.thingpedia.weather.current ) filter param:wind_speed <= NUMBER_0 unit:mph => notify ; now => @com.twitter.post ;

column3: unfollow something on twitter when integer is greater than NUMBER_0 .
column4: $dialogue @org.thingpedia.dialogue.transaction.execute ; now => ( @org.thingpedia.builtin.thingengine.builtin.get_random_between ) filter param:random >= NUMBER_0 => notify ; now => @com.twitter.unfollow ;

column3: if the amount is higher than NUMBER_0 then do n't follow on twitter
column4: $dialogue @org.thingpedia.dialogue.transaction.execute ; now => ( @org.thingpedia.builtin.thingengine.builtin.get_random_between ) filter param:random >= NUMBER_0 => notify ; now => @com.twitter.unfollow ;

column3: show the current weather then say QUOTED_STRING_0 .
show the current local weather then state : QUOTED_STRING_0 .
column4: $dialogue @org.thingpedia.dialogue.transaction.execute ; now => @org.thingpedia.weather.current param:location = location:current_location => notify ; now => @org.thingpedia.builtin.thingengine.builtin.say param:message = QUOTED_STRING_0 ;

column3: show the weather and say QUOTED_STRING_0 .
when you are searching twitter for HASHTAG_0 look for hashtags that have HASHTAG_1 and QUOTED_STRING_0
column4: $dialogue @org.thingpedia.dialogue.transaction.execute ; now => ( @com.twitter.tweet ) filter param:hashtags contains HASHTAG_0 and param:hashtags contains HASHTAG_1 => notify ; now => @org.thingpedia.builtin.thingengine.builtin.say param:message = QUOTED_STRING_0 ;

column3: search twitter using the term HASHTAG_0 and if it also has hashtag HASHTAG_1 then say QUOTED_STRING_0
column4: $dialogue @org.thingpedia.dialogue.transaction.execute ; now => ( @com.twitter.tweet ) filter param:hashtags contains HASHTAG_0 and param:hashtags contains HASHTAG_1 => notify ; now => @org.thingpedia.builtin.thingengine.builtin.say param:message = QUOTED_STRING_0 ;

column3: look up HASHTAG_0 with HASHTAG_1 on twitter and put QUOTED_STRING_0
column4: $dialogue @org.thingpedia.dialogue.transaction.execute ; now => ( @com.twitter.tweet ) filter param:hashtags contains HASHTAG_0 and param:hashtags contains HASHTAG_1 => notify ; now => @org.thingpedia.builtin.thingengine.builtin.say param:message = QUOTED_STRING_0 ;

column3: find HASHTAG_0 with HASHTAG_1 on twitter , and say QUOTED_STRING_0
column4: $dialogue @org.thingpedia.dialogue.transaction.execute ; now => ( @com.twitter.tweet ) filter param:hashtags contains HASHTAG_0 and param:hashtags contains HASHTAG_1 => notify ; now => @org.thingpedia.builtin.thingengine.builtin.say param:message = QUOTED_STRING_0 ;
